        "preview_url":  "https://images.steamusercontent.com/ugc/10892521643278143698/DCA70FAEDED7064B3D1D49E33B3C035040CCE6E2/",
        "hcontent_preview":  "10892521643278143698",
        "title":  "Fall Guys Level [QOL UPDATE]",
        "description":  "This is my first level for MECCHA CHARMELEON and it\u0027s Fall Guys themed.\r\n\r\nIf there\u0027s any problem or feedback please let me know!\r\n\r\nbtw don\u0027t forget to play fall guys lol please let this game alive :(\r\n\r\n[QOL UPDATE]\r\n\r\n- Added X-Ray Material support (huge thanks to RareKiwi on Discord)\r\n\r\n- Relocated spawn point to prevent issues\r\n\r\n- Adjusted lighting to look more polished than previous\r\n\r\nand more stuffs i can\u0027t remember or maybe that\u0027s all...\r\n\r\nHope you enjoy and Thanks for playing!\r\n\r\n\r\n-------------\r\n\r\nFAQ\r\n\r\n\r\nQ : People are getting black screen and fell off from the level! What do I do with this situation?\r\nA : Make sure to check if everyone downloaded every level correctly or else the game won\u0027t able to load the level and output blank space and fell off from the level.\r\n\r\nQ : This level has a terrible performance ! Fix your level !\r\nA : I tested this level with UHD Graphics 770 (which is 11% better than GTS 450, released in 2010) and it\u0027s getting about 20 fps on highest settings, 30 fps on lowest settings.\r\n\r\nIf you\u0027re getting worse fps than this then it\u0027s either your pc\u0027s problem or the game settings problem. \r\n\r\nPlease refrain to say about performance issue if you have low-end specs pc.\r\n\r\nQ : I\u0027m keep getting thru into inside of some platforms (or There\u0027s an issue with collisions) thus it\u0027s unplayable\r\nA : I tested all collisions and there was no issue at all.\r\n\r\nBut since I\u0027m a human so I can\u0027t test everything perfectly, there could be an issue about it.\r\n\r\nIf you have encountered collision issues, please report them on \r\ndiscussions with screenshot (or else i won\u0027t be able to address about it, most of time when there\u0027s an issue i can\u0027t reproduce it because i have no idea about it)\r\n\r\nAlso, unexpected collision issue could happen if you have low-spec pc or bad network.",
