        "title":  "Courage the Cowardly Dog  [v1.4.2]",
        "description":  "The Bagge family farmhouse from Courage the Cowardly Dog.\r\n\r\nThe outside will be accessible once the inside is good, I am slowly adding things outside to make it less empty, there is almost nothing outside right now.\r\n\r\nSometimes I might stream me developing the map on twitch\r\n@nordbo_\r\n\r\nThank you to the streamers over on twitch who have given feedback and support on the map \r\n\r\n@bailibytes\r\n@ashIV_\r\n@xHalFPSx\r\n@ActionJaxon\r\n\r\nAnd everyone in the comments who have been giving feedback, I really appreciate it!\r\n\r\nI have uploaded a new map\r\nhttps://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3749677184\r\nThe mystery shack from Gravity Falls!\r\n\r\nCredits:\r\nModel can be found here:\r\nsketchfab.com/3d-models/courage-the-cowardly-dog-bagge-farmhouse-584f0d2e5d32457198b7dc9a3894b88a\r\n\r\nThis map is still a WIP!\r\nWhile a lot has been done (mostly optimizing and fixing the models) my main goal right now is to populate the map with more props that makes sense.\r\n\r\nThat being said, now that most issues have been addressed and (hopefully) fixed I can now start focusing on populating inside the house and outside.",
